data.description: Spacious and move-in ready home one mile from Whiting Field! This beautiful contemporary is conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, and schools in a quiet Milton subdivision. With nearly 2,300 square feet including four bedrooms, two full baths, and an office, it's a perfect place to raise a growing family. Walking in you're greeted with a large foyer with a formal dining room and an office/study on either side. Flowing tile floors take you into the grand family room which features vaulted ceilings, a tile fireplace, and sliding doors to screened porch. From the family room is access to beautiful kitchen. It provides ample storage with the center island and corner pantry, and numerous upgrades like white cabinets, subway tile backsplash, and 1 year old energy efficient stainless steel appliances including an air fryer/convection oven. Split from the guest bedrooms and bathroom is the private primary suite. With views of the backyard and an amazing ensuite bathroom, it's a true oasis. Speaking of the amazing ensuite, it has a double vanity, jetted tub and separate shower, and his AND hers walk-in closets! Out back is a fully privacy yard for the kids and pets to safely play while you relax on the screened porch. Other awesome features included with this home are the backyard shed, two car garage, plantation shutters throughout, and ADT security system! Roof to be replaced prior to closing with acceptable offer.
